to take care of it.

762
00:35:49.286 --> 00:35:51.355
but she wasn't hearing
any of that.

763
00:35:51.455 --> 00:35:52.823
Of course.

764
00:35:55.159 --> 00:35:57.695
And then my mom found out.

765
00:35:57.795 --> 00:35:59.997
So I had to do right.

766
00:36:00.130 --> 00:36:02.667
You don't even know
how many times

767
00:36:02.767 --> 00:36:06.370
I actually prayed to be free.

768
00:36:07.304 --> 00:36:09.774
And so your prayers
were answered.

769
00:36:09.874 --> 00:36:11.842
No.

770
00:36:14.311 --> 00:36:16.881
Look. I know
I'm not a good guy...

771
00:36:17.682 --> 00:36:19.516
...but I swear to God...

772
00:36:20.350 --> 00:36:22.452
...I'm not a bad guy. either.

773
00:36:29.159 --> 00:36:30.795
Honestly?

774
00:36:30.861 --> 00:36:33.664
I'm not sure what the hell
I'm looking at here.

775
00:36:33.764 --> 00:36:35.399
Assuming what you said before...

776
00:36:35.532 --> 00:36:37.702
