Kaliyah got everything
she wanted.

910
00:42:50.840 --> 00:42:51.841
Ryleigh.

911
00:42:51.976 --> 00:42:53.843
Everything.

912
00:42:53.978 --> 00:42:57.114
And I got the scraps.

913
