915
00:43:01.685 --> 00:43:03.988
And...

916
00:43:04.088 --> 00:43:06.823
in the end. still...

917
00:43:07.791 --> 00:43:09.826
...she picked Kaliyah...

918
00:43:10.727 --> 00:43:12.662
...over me.

919
00:43:12.796 --> 00:43:15.299
Ryleigh. No...

920
00:43:21.771 --> 00:43:23.673
Ryleigh.

921
00:43:23.773 --> 00:43:24.874
No.

922
